  "title": "Hairstylist | Hair Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide professional hair services including cutting, wash &amp; blow, coloring/highlighting, and hair &amp; scalp treatments.</li>\n  <li>Conduct hair and scalp analysis, and introduce suitable products and services to clients.</li>\n  <li>Explain treatment processes and demonstrate product features and benefits clearly to clients.</li>\n  <li>Recommend and assist clients in selecting the most suitable retail products and services for their hair and scalp care needs.</li>\n  <li>Deliver excellent customer service with professionalism and care, building lasting client relationships.</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1–2 years of relevant experience in hair styling and/or scalp therapy.</li>\n  <li>Candidates with no prior experience are welcome to apply for a trainee position (training will be provided).</li>\n</ul>",
